      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FURIOUS FALCON (1) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at this track over 510m behind GAS AND DUST (29.10) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at his previous run. Looks the one to beat on his best form. TALCOTT BALE (8) finished third last start over 450m at Shepparton but was game in defeat in a useful 25.25. Has the ability and looks a key chance. FAST FREDDY (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at Sandown in a handy 29.86 beating Hey Presto. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Expecting another bold showing. GAS AND DUST (7) scored by 4.5 lengths last time (28.64) in a Grade 4/5 over 510m at this track. Has already won three times from this draw.",
